#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/cssi.rst:2
msgid "CSS 注入"
msgstr "CSS Injection"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/cssi.rst:5
msgid "基本介绍"
msgstr "Basic Introduction"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/cssi.rst:6
msgid ""
"CSS注入最早开始于利用CSS中的 ``expression()`` ``url()`` ``regex()`` "
"等函数或特性来引入外部的恶意代码，但是随着浏览器的发展，这种方式被逐渐禁用，与此同时，出现了一些新的攻击方式。"
msgstr ""
"CSS injection originally involved using CSS functions or features such as "
"``expression()``, ``url()``, and ``regex()`` to introduce external malicious "
"code. As browsers evolved, this approach was gradually disabled, while some "
"new attack methods appeared."

