msgid "当可以插入CSS的时候，可以使用 ``font-face`` 配合 ``unicode-range`` 获取目标网页对应字符集。PoC如下"
msgstr ""
"When CSS can be inserted, ``font-face`` can be combined with "
"``unicode-range`` to obtain the character set used by the target page. The "
"PoC is as follows:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/cssi.rst:53
msgid "当字符较多时，则可以结合 ``::first-line``  等CSS属性缩小范围，以获取更精确的内容"
msgstr ""
"When there are many characters, CSS features such as ``::first-line`` can be "
"used to narrow the range and obtain more precise content"
